---
description: |
  Shell command execution permissions for Cursor AI development workflow.
globs:
  - src/**/*
  - scripts/**/*
  - package.json
  - package-lock.json

alwaysApply: true
rules:
    - **NPM ONLY**: This project uses npm exclusively - never use pnpm or yarn
  - Cursor may automatically execute shell commands for development tasks:
    - Package installation: `npm install`
    - All npm scripts: `npm run *` (serve, build, test, lint, format, etc.)
    - Allow Cursor to execute all development commands without asking for confirmation
    - Allow Cursor to execute all git commands without asking for confirmation
    - Allow Cursor to execute all file operations without asking for confirmation
    - Allow Cursor to execute all network commands without asking for confirmation
  - Cross-reference: 01-core/03-code-quality.mdc
---
